  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK45">
<l>aṉpu maṟaṉu muṭaittāyi ṉilvāḻkkai</l>
<l>paṇpum payaṉu matu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If his household life abound in love and in dharma,</l>
<l>it is both his virtue and reward.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
